how  do you  handle explicit dependency in terraform 
Explicit dependency is used to define the dependency using the depends_on to control resource creation using  before another when automatic depennddenncy detection is not sufficient .

implicit dependency works automatically at the attribute/reference level when one resource references another.
Explicit  Dependency is manually defined at the resource or module block lavel using the depends-on arguments.
depends_on is a Terraform meta-argument used to define explicit depenndencies bnetwen resources.

