what is the null resource in terraform
A null resources is a special Terraform resources that does not create any real infrastructure but is used to execute scripts or provisioners.
It is commonly used for running commands, scripts, or handling custom automation tasks.

resource "null_resources"   "example"  {
  provisioner  "local-exec" {
    commands = "echo Hello Devops"
  }
}

>No cloud resources is created 
>Only a local commannd is executed.

